    <div id="intro">
      <h2>Introduction</h2>
      <p>
        This document describes the <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/XInclude">XInclude</a>
        namespace <code>http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude</code>. This namespace name may be 
        reused in any update of the specification which is made for the purpose of 
        clarification or bug fixes. These changes will be minor in that they do not (a) 
        change the meaning or validity of existing documents written using the 
        namespace, or (b) affect the operation of existing software written to process 
        such documents.</p>
    </div>
